cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to enhance the resolution of thermal images using visible-range images as a guide. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) another likely category. The paper proposes a novel algorithm that explicitly tackles the issue of texture-mismatch caused due to multimodality, which involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper also involves the use of neural networks, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Finally, the paper involves the use of edge-extraction and integration techniques, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics).
